<section class="rbp-membership-model" aria-label="Membership operating model">
  <div class="rbp-membership-model__inner page-width">
    <div class="rbp-membership-model__intro">
      <div class="rbp-membership-model__eyebrow">Confirmed membership model</div>
      <h2>Premium Member access, powered through Shopify Subscriptions</h2>
      <p>Membership access is based on the customer tag <strong>Premium Member</strong>. Subscription billing is handled through Shopify Subscriptions, while payment-plan administration is supported through Shopify Subscriptions and actioned independently where required.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="rbp-membership-model__grid">
      <div class="rbp-membership-model__card">
        <span>01</span>
        <h3>Access tag</h3>
        <p>Customers with the <strong>Premium Member</strong> tag are recognised as active members across the account and member portal experience.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rbp-membership-model__card">
        <span>02</span>
        <h3>Subscription billing</h3>
        <p>Membership billing should be managed through Shopify Subscriptions so billing, renewals and subscription status stay aligned with Shopify.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rbp-membership-model__card">
        <span>03</span>
        <h3>Payment plans</h3>
        <p>Payment plan management is facilitated through Shopify Subscriptions, with operational handling and support actioned independently where needed.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rbp-membership-model__card">
        <span>04</span>
        <h3>Member resources</h3>
        <p>The member-only resource area is scaffolded now. Actual premium-only content can be added later without rebuilding the portal architecture.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<style>
.rbp-membership-model{background:#f8fafc;padding:72px 0}.rbp-membership-model__inner{display:grid;gap:26px}.rbp-membership-model__intro{max-width:850px}.rbp-membership-model__eyebrow{display:inline-flex;border-radius:999px;background:#dbeafe;color:#1d4ed8;padding:7px 12px;font-size:12px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase}.rbp-membership-model h2{margin:14px 0 0;color:#0f172a;font-size:clamp(30px,4vw,50px);line-height:1.06;letter-spacing:-.035em;font-weight:900}.rbp-membership-model p{margin:14px 0 0;color:#64748b;line-height:1.7;font-size:15px}.rbp-membership-model__grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,minmax(0,1fr));gap:18px}.rbp-membership-model__card{background:#fff;border:1px solid rgba(15,23,42,.1);border-radius:24px;padding:22px;box-shadow:0 1px 2px rgba(15,23,42,.05)}.rbp-membership-model__card span{width:42px;height:42px;border-radius:15px;background:#dbeafe;color:#1d4ed8;display:grid;place-items:center;font-weight:900;margin-bottom:14px}.rbp-membership-model__card h3{margin:0 0 8px;color:#0f172a;font-size:18px;font-weight:900}.rbp-membership-model__card p{font-size:14px;margin:0}@media(max-width:989px){.rbp-membership-model__grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,minmax(0,1fr))}}@media(max-width:749px){.rbp-membership-model{padding:54px 0}.rbp-membership-model__grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
</style>
